      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul (water pump, thermostat, and expansion tank) and a comprehensive subframe inspection to ensure structural rigidity. The engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline with the characteristic metallic rasp, and the hydraulic steering rack provides exceptional tactile feedback. A well-maintained performance icon ready for the twisties.",
